  ledger.ledgerWorker.ledgerReprocessamentoMessageProcessor -> ledger.ledgerWorker.ledgerWorkerApplication "Envia ProcessarReprocessamentoLancamentosCommand" "MediatR"
  ledger.ledgerWorker.ledgerReprocessamentoMessageProcessor -> ledger.ledgerDb "Atualiza status e registra eventos finais no Outbox" "EF Core / SQL"

